Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 
28. Rāgapeyyāla 
276. Iddhipādasutta 
“Rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya cattāro dhammā bhāvetabbā. 
Katame cattāro? 
Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu chandasamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti; 
vīriyasamādhi … pe … cittasamādhi … pe … vīmaṃsāsamādhipadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti. 
Rāgassa, bhikkhave, abhiññāya ime cattāro dhammā bhāvetabbā”ti. 
Tatiyaṃ. 
